# Frontend Design System Rules

When editing or creating components in `frontend/src/components/`:

## Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS only; no CSS Modules during/after design migration
- Color palette: `sage-*`, `olive-*`, `scenario-cash`, `scenario-financed`, `scenario-rental`, `status-success`, `status-error`, `status-warning`, `status-info`
- Typography: `.text-h1`, `.text-h2`, `.text-h3`, `.text-body`, `.text-small`, `.text-currency` (from index.css)

## Import Paths

- **Organisms** (`organisms/X/`): import from `../../atoms`, `../../molecules`
- **Molecules** (`molecules/X/`): import from `../../atoms`
- **Atoms** (`atoms/X/`): import from sibling atoms, e.g. `../Spinner`, `../Icon`

## Component Hierarchy

- **Atoms:** Icon, Spinner, Label, Tooltip, Input, Button, Card (no dependencies on other atoms except Button→Spinner, Tooltip→Icon)
- **Molecules:** InputField = Label + Input + optional Tooltip + Error/Helper
- **Organisms:** Header, Footer, CalculatorForm, ComparisonResults, CostComparisonChart

## Types

- Use types from `frontend/src/types/calculation.types.ts` (CalculationInput, CalculationResponse, etc.)
- Never use `any` for calculation or API data

